File order:
	$HOME/.zshenv      - sets $ZDOTDIR
	$ZDOTDIR/.zprofile - linked to shared $HOME/.profile; run only at login
	                     startx needs to be run before p10k starts, or else $TTY gets fucked and X can't find the console
	$ZDOTDIR/.zshrc    - all the configuration
	$ZDOTDIR/.zlogin   - unused; custom .profile for only zsh
	$ZDOTDIR/.zlogout  - unused
